title: Nobody Cares: Passion & Protest Won't Save the Planet. (vegan / vegans / veganism)
description: "Effective Activism" has nothing to do with passion: showing people how upset you are (or how much you care) is not a winning strategy in the context of democratic pluralism --especially not when you represent a despised minority (like veganism).
